 2023-11882023-12-01AAFC
ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectOrder providing for assistance to Saskatchewan beekepers
PrecisOrder authorizing Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food Canada to enter into the AGREEMENT with the province of Saskatchewan to provide federal contributions of up to $642,000 under the AGRICULTURAL DISASTER RELIEF PROGRAM (AgriRecovery) to assist the beekeepers with the extraordinary costs incurred as a result of the extreme cold temperatures of the winter of 2021-2022.
